d Frame</div><div class="specs-item-content"><p>Aluminum, nickel-free chrome plated</p></div></div></div></div><div class="row min-margin-top no-margin-xs"><div class="em-xs-12 em-md-4"><div class="specs-item"><div class="specs-item-title">Stretchable Band</div><div class="specs-item-content"><p>Polyester: 80%</p><p>Polyurethane: 20%</p><p>Aluminum, nickel-free chrome plated buckle</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="row low-margin-bottom"><div class="em-xs-12 em-md-2"><div class="bold title-color">Dimensions</div></div><div class="em-xs-12 em-md-10"><div class="specs-wrapper"><div class="row"><div class="em-xs-12 em-md-4"><div class="specs-item"><div class="specs-item-title">Embrace</div><div class="specs-item-content"><p>Length: 37.6mm (1.480&quot;)</p><p>Width: 29.7mm (1.169&quot;)</p><p>Height: 10.3mm (4.055&quot;)</p><p>Weight: 13g (0.459oz)</p></div></div></div><div class="em-xs-12 em-md-4"><div class="specs-item"><div class="specs-item-title">Stretchable Band</div><div class="specs-item-content"><p>Spring bar: 27 mm (fits 24 mm watch bands)</p><p>Min Circumference: 100 mm (3.937&quot;)</p><p>Max Circumference: 200 mm (7.874&quot;)</p><p>Width: 24mm (0.945&quot;)</p></div></div></div><div class="em-xs-12 em-md-4"><div class="specs-item"><div class="specs-item-title">USB Charging Dock</div><div class="specs-item-content"><p>Length: 48.0mm (1.809&quot;)</p><p>Width: 31.0mm (1.220&quot;)</p><p>Height: 21.0mm (0.827&quot;)</p></div></div></div></div><div class="row min-margin-top no-margin-xs"><div class="em-xs-12 em-md-4"><div class="specs-item"><div class="specs-item-title">USB Cable</div><div class="specs-item-content"><p>Length: 180mm (7.087&quot;)</p><p>Connection type 1 (Micro USB B, male)</p><p>Connection type 2 (USB A, male)</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="row low-margin-bottom"><div class="em-xs-12 em-md-2"><div class="bold title-color">Components</div></div><div class="em-xs-12 em-md-10"><div class="specs-wrapper"><div class="row"><div class="em-xs-12 em-md-4"><div class="specs-item"><div class="specs-item-title">Sensors</div><div class="specs-item-content"><p>EDA Sensor</p><p>Peripheral Temperature Sensor</p><p>3-Axis accelerometer</p><p>Gyroscope</p></div></div></div><div class="em-xs-12 em-md-4"><div class="specs-item"><div class="specs-item-title">Display &amp; Feedback</div><div class="specs-item-content"><p>Capacitive touch-button interface</p><p>12-sector ring of multicolor Light Emitting Diodes (LEDs)</p><p>Vibration motor for alerts and alarms</p></div></div></div><div class="em-xs-12 em-md-4"><div class="specs-item"><div class="specs-item-title">Battery</div><div class="specs-item-content"><p>3.7V Li-ion</p><p>Minimum capacity of 90 mAh</p><p>Charge time: 2 hours</p></div></div></div></div><div class="row min-margin-top no-margin-xs"><div class="em-xs-12 em-md-4"><div class="specs-item"><div class="specs-item-title">Charger</div><div class="specs-item-content"><p>Input Voltage: 5 V</p><p>Output Current: 100 mA</p><p>Micro USB B, female connector (charge only, no data transfer)</p></div></div></div><div class="em-xs-12 em-md-4"><div class="specs-item"><div class="specs-item-title">Memory</div><div class="specs-item-content"><p>Flash Memory - 8 Mbit</p></div></div></div><div class="em-xs-12 em-md-4"><div class="specs-item"><div class="specs-item-title">Radio Transceiver</div><div class="specs-item-content"><p>Bluetooth Low Energy Smart®</p></div></div></div></div><div class="row min-margin-top no-margin-xs"></div></div></div></div><div class="row low-margin-bottom"><div class="em-xs-12 em-md-2"><div class="bold title-color">Environmental Conditions</div></div><div class="em-xs-12 em-md-10"><div class="specs-wrapper"><div class="row"><div class="em-xs-12 em-md-4"><div class="specs-item"><div class="specs-item-title">Water Resistance</div><div class="specs-item-content"><p>Embrace is water resistant (IP67 standard)</p><p>Embrace is protected from immersion up to 1 meter</p></div></div></div><div class="em-xs-12 em-md-4"><div class="specs-item"><div class="specs-item-title">Temperature Range</div><div class="specs-item-content"><p>-20°C +70°C</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="section-separator"></div><div class="section section-collapse" id="embrace-faq"><h2><button class="toggle-collapse" data-target="embrace-faq"></button> <span class="toggle-collapse" data-target="embrace-faq">FAQ</span></h2><div class="collapse"><div class="row"><div class="em-xs-12 em-sm-6"><div class="low-padding-right no-padding-xs"><div class="bold title-color">Which phones and tablets do the Embrace Apps work with?</div><div class=""><p class="min-margin-bottom">Any iOS device supporting Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE / 4.0 / Bluetooth Smart) that can run iOS 9.3.5 or higher.</p><p class="min-margin-bottom">Any Android devices running Android version 5.0 (Lollipop) or higher, as long as they support Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE / 4.0 / Bluetooth Smart)</p><p class="min-margin-bottom">We do not support Windows and BlackBerry phones.</p></div></div></div><div class="em-xs-12 em-sm-6"><div class="low-padding-right no-padding-xs"><div class="bold title-color">Can Embrace detect any type of seizure?</div><div class=""><p class="min-margin-bottom">The machine learning algorithms running in the Embrace are trained on generalized convulsive seizures. Embrace is optimized to detect events that involve both unusual motor activity and autonomic activation.</p><p class="min-margin-bottom">Complex partial seizures usually do not generate convulsions, so we would not expect Embrace to detect these types of seizures.</p><p class="min-margin-bottom">Absence seizures do not generate significant autonomic or motion responses, therefore we would not expect Embrace to detect these seizures.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="row"><div class="em-xs-12 em-sm-6"><div class="low-padding-right no-padding-xs"><div class="bold title-color">How does the Embrace work?</div><div class=""><p class="min-margin-bottom">Embrace needs to be paired with a compatible smartphone with Internet access and always stay within its Bluetooth® range.</p><p class="min-margin-bottom">The paired phone must remain in close proximity to the individual wearing the Embrace (under ~10m or 30 feet). Only in this case will it be able to send alert calls/SMS to the active caregivers when Embrace detects a convulsive seizure.</p></div></div></div><div class="em-xs-12 em-sm-6"><div class="low-padding-right no-padding-xs"><div class="bold title-color">How does the Embrace Alert System work?</div><div class=""><p class="min-margin-bottom">Embrace sends data to the paired smartphone via Bluetooth®, and from the smartphone to Empatica’s servers via Internet connection. When Embrace detects a possible convulsive seizure, it will send Alert calls and SMS to the caregiver’s phones. In order to do this, Embrace must be within Bluetooth range (10m/30 ft) of it’s paired phone.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="row"></div></div></div><div class="section-separator"></div><!-- MD --><div id="embrace-accessories"><div class="section hidden-xs"><h2 class="text-center">Personalize your Embrace</h2><!-- bands --><div class="accessory extra-light-grey-background low-margin-bottom"><table><tr><td class="accessory-image"><img class="store-img v-40904724931" alt="Embrace Band" src="https://www.empatica.com/assets/images/products/cart_band_milan_black.png"> <img class="store-img v-40904724995" alt="Embrace Band" src="https://www.empatica.com/assets/images/products/cart_band_boston_blue.png"> <img class="store-img v-40904724867" alt="Embrace Band" src="https://www.empatica.com/assets/images/products/cart_band_seoul_grey.png"></td><td class="accessory-details"><div class="title">Stretchable Bands</div><div>Maintains skin contact required for physiological signal capture. Fits both adults and children (Wrist/ankle circumference XS-L: 10~20 cm 3.93~7.78 in; 